Hi Nick

> -1 ($FFFFFFFF). Possibly blitz is using a signed byte instread of unsigned?

Yup, Blitz assumes signed values for everything.
You can do this to get the correct values:
    blah.w = Peek.b(&wherever) & $FFFF

That will get you 0-125 and 255.


